text: @realDonaldTrump "The problem with the world is that fools and fanatics are always so certain of themselves, and wiser people so full of doubts." - Bertrand Russell

The fact that you retweet TV ratings en route to a G7 meeting summarizes your presidency. You are out of touch and out of your mind. You are an ego maniacal fool who unfortunately is the leader of the Free World. Your behavior hurts our society, our markets and our economy.
